             was indicted for <rs id="t18031026-25-off140" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18031026-25-off140" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18031026-25-off140" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18031026-25-cd141" type="crimeDate">19th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18031026-25-off140 t18031026-25-cd141"></join>, a copper, value 30s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18031026-25-victim218" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Richards
               <interp inst="t18031026-25-victim218" type="surname" value="Richards"></interp>
